    <item>
      <title>Open Multiple Shells</title>
      <link>/2015/12/03/open-multiple-shells/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Dec 2015 00:00:00 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2015/12/03/open-multiple-shells/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Once you have the &lt;code&gt;shell&lt;/code&gt; layer enabled, you can open multiple shells by using
