    <item>
      <title>Stop Cursor Creep</title>
      <link>/2015/12/01/stop-cursor-creep/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Dec 2015 00:00:00 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2015/12/01/stop-cursor-creep/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Does it bother you that the cursor creeps back when you go back to normal mode?
Well, there&amp;rsquo;s a setting for that. Put &lt;code&gt;(setq evil-move-cursor-back nil)&lt;/code&gt; in your
config, and it&amp;rsquo;ll stop doing that.&lt;/p&gt;

