    <item>
      <title>Refocus Helm</title>
      <link>/2015/10/20/refocus-helm/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Oct 2015 00:00:00 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2015/10/20/refocus-helm/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Sometimes when Helm loses focus, it breaks a little bit (try clicking outside
the helm buffer to see what I mean.) If this happens, you&amp;rsquo;ve got two options:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;start another helm session (which will kill the existing buffer)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;use &lt;code&gt;switch-to-minibuffer-window&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;code&gt;SPC w b&lt;/code&gt;) to refocus your session&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

